{"tid":1874322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恥爽：若《華爾街日報》不對歉，我口交","createTime":"2020-02-11T06:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T10:08:08.000Z","uid":42188,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b68b5503c20bd58c587c53b387cd36755c67d9a1","tid":1874322,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，已經就美國《華爾街日報》發表辱華的文章，向報社提出嚴正交涉，要求報章認識到錯誤的嚴重性，公開正式道歉，並查處相關責任人，但報社至今仍在敷衍、推搪，敦促報社正視中方關切，嚴肅回應中方的要求，<span style=\"color: red;\">中方保留對報社進一步採取措施的權利</span>。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》網站，日前發布由美國的保守派外交學者米德撰寫題為「中國是真正的亞洲病夫」的評論文章，文章以借新型冠狀病毒疫情，比喻中國的經濟和發展前景，文章認為，中國的金融市場可能比中國華南野生動物市場更危險，中國的實力雖然令人矚目，但仍然很脆弱，更具致命性的「病毒」或在金融市場蔓延，可能隨時改變中國的經濟和政治前景，又揚言中國的經濟就將今次的疫情一樣，將會崩潰或出現不可遏制的後果等。"},{"pid":"1a459f14f665eb7c6f87ec077c7026dbe1f86d9c","tid":1874322,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喺屋企家居隔離緊？<br />\n無口罩出唔到街？<br />\n咁快啲過嚟<span style=\"color: blue;\">Twitter</span>戰線！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要光復香港撳幾個掣都唔得？</span></span><br />\nTwitterHelpBot嘅tasklist 24小時更新<br />\n入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=de0389b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">RT + Like + Comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. Rick Scott <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1226912446767562759?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1226912446767562759%3Fs%3D09&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=b0d9fab3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=h